text: This is a list of Governors of Nagano Prefecture: *Kaneyoshi Tachiki 1871–1873 *Hironao Narasaki 1873–1881 *Makoto Ono 1881–1884 *Seiichi Kinashi 1884–1889 *Utsumi Tadakatsu 1889–1891 *Asada Tokunori 1891–1896 *Chikaaki Takasaki 1896–1897 *Kan'ichi Gondo 1897–1898 *1898–1899 Isamu Sonoyama *1899–1902 Norikichi Oshikawa *1902–1905 Kiyohide Seki *1905–1911 Tsunamasa Ōyama *1911–1913 Teikan Chiba *Ichiro Yoda 1913–1914 *1914–1915 Yūichirō Chikaraishi *1915–1921 Tenta Akaboshi *1921–1922 Tadahiko Okada *1922–1924 Toshio Honma *1924–1926 Mitsusada Umetani *1926–1927 Morio Takahashi *1927–1929 Ryo Chiba *1929–1931 Shintarō Suzuki *1931–1933 Kuraji Ishigaki *1933–1935 Shōzō Okada *Seiichi Ōmura 1935–1936 *Shunsuke Kondo 1936–1938 *January 11–December 23, 1938 Seiichi Ōmura *1938–1940 Kenji Tomita *1940–1942 Minoru Suzuki *1942–1943 Hakuji Nagayasu *1943–1944 Yoshio Kōriyama *1944–1945 Yasuo Ōtsubo *1945–1947 Kunrō Mononobe *March–April 1947 Yoshio Iyoku *1947–1959 Torao Hayashi *1959–1980 Gon'ichirō Nishizawa *1980–2000 Goro Yoshimura *Yasuo Tanaka 2000–2006 *Jin Murai 2006–2010 *Shuichi Abe 2010– Category:Governors of Nagano
title: List of governors of Nagano Prefecture
